{"tid":260170,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【連登公投】正評阿仙奴 負評車路士","createTime":"2017-05-27T13:35:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-27T18:37:09.000Z","uid":45772,"like":21,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"01727ed8dcea7203945e807f429c62dad67f6028","tid":260170,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T13:35:25.000Z","msg":"【連登公投】正評阿仙奴 負評車路士"},{"pid":"5e2ca121a3afbe06edadcdf28b6775747faf6c24","tid":260170,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T13:44:28.000Z","msg":"這時雲加山狗奧燒，已與干地的夏世三拆到二百招以上。兩隊踢法家數截然不同，但均是愈鬥力氣愈長，球影腳風，籠蓋了溫布萊之頂，球迷叫上來的聲音直攻入領隊二人耳中。雲加雖無法比，始終不落下風。干地激鬥中覺得干堤微微搖晃，心知343陣法為基奧特衝擊，頃刻間便要倒台，那時勢必和雲加、車迷同歸於盡，又見阿仙奴戰術越變越奇，再鬥百餘招只怕便要為雲加所製"},{"pid":"716e9b40fd960745a44a889318bf0594b9361af0","tid":260170,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T13:47:01.000Z","msg":"預言 ：基奧特絕殺車路士"},{"pid":"49ae17db2556a5b58c79aa0b9ffbe9969a3d286a","tid":260170,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T14:23:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a47b6a0aa7becdd77cf82df54f293eca29f3b90","tid":260170,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T18:37:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>預言 ：基奧特絕殺車路士</blockquote><br />\n啱"}]}